        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "The Shoop Shoop Show - The Cher Collection"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Get ready to experience a Cher show like no other – heading to theatres across the UK, Europe and Canada in 2026!\n\n‘Turn Back Time’ with The Shoop Shoop Show - The Cher Collection, an exhilarating music-led production with a party atmosphere. It is led by international powerhouse vocalist Rachael Hawnt, the winner of ITV’s Starstruck.\n\nThe show spans every decade of Cher’s incredible career so be prepared to be dazzled by disco HITS and pop rock chart-toppers. As the show unfolds Rachael’s spot-on impersonation will make you ‘Believe’."
      }
    ]
